high_descs: Turn to the left and head across to the counter left of the stove.
Open the cabinet under that counter and pick up the blue plate in that cabinet.
Turn right and bring the plate to the microwave.
Heat the plate in the microwave.
Take the heated plate to the cabinet on the right.
Put the plate in the cabinet on the right in the corner.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated plate in the corner cabinet.

high_descs: Turn left and head towards the counter to the left of the stove.
Open the cabinet below the counter and take out a blue plate
Take a step to the right towards the microwave above the stove.
Heat up the plate and take it back out of the microwave.
Turn right and face the cabinet below the wine bottle.
Open the cabinet and place the plate inside.
anns.task_desc: Place a warm blue plate in the cabinet beneath the wine bottle.

high_descs: Turn around to walk halfway to the counter and then turn to the right and walk towards the counter next to the stove.
Open the cupboard below the counter and take out the blue plate.
Turn right slightly and then left to bring the plate up to the microwave.
Open the microwave and place the plate inside then shut the door. Open the door and take the plate back out.
Turn to the right and look down.
Open the cupboard straight ahead on the left and place the plate inside and shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Take out the blue plate place it in the microwave to put it away again.
